3740:SynaptiX_FDK/services/littlefs/lfs.c **** 
3741:SynaptiX_FDK/services/littlefs/lfs.c ****     // if we're only reading and our new offset is still in the file's cache
3742:SynaptiX_FDK/services/littlefs/lfs.c ****     // we can avoid flushing and needing to reread the data
